(320, 'St.Georg im Schauertal', '2026-08-20', 1.5, 2, 3, 'Georg932', 48.102833, 13.969417, '<p>Since my cache in Wels (Operation Wels) disappeared <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_sad.gif" /> ,i have to do some pilgrimage to get <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_maint.gif" /> of my sins.</p> <p>What fits better then a pilgrimage church in a locality named same as my hometown <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_cool.gif" />.</p> <p>First i think about a hard <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/WptTypes/8.gif" /> - but then a voice: "There are so many new Cachers out there -<img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_tongue.gif" /> for caches!"</p> <p>So it"s a <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/WptTypes/2.gif" /> , and you don"t have to be <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_shock.gif" /> : "No, another <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_evil.gif" /> NPG!"</p> <p>Maybe, the coordinates <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_dead.gif" /> : look at the door, there 4 great digits on a note: create the highest possible amount of degree (no, it"s nothing to melt, so you know what i mean <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_wink.gif" />) Follow this direction 13 meters to the cache - <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_cool.gif" />.</p> <p>to visit the church you got the key by the neighbors btw. read it on the list at the door!</p> <p>happy hunting <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_cool.gif" /></p> <p><em>So time to think about a new <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_evil.gif" /><img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_sad.gif" /> <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_dead.gif" /><img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_shock.gif" /> <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_angry.gif" /><img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_dissapprove.gif" /> cache <img src="http://www.geocaching.com/images/icons/icon_smile_clown.gif" /></em></p> <p><em>&copy; <a href="http://www.opencaching.de/viewprofile.php?userid=101129">npg</a>, <a href="http://www.opencaching.de/viewcache.php?cacheid=112244">Opencaching.de</a>, <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0/de/">CC-BY-NC-ND</a>, Stand: 14.10.2013; alle Logeinträge &copy; jeweiliger Autor</em></p>'),
